      <title>奈拉再创历史新低，尼日利亚企业削减美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/-usd-ngn-nigerian-firms-slim-down-dollar-debt-as-naira-hits-another-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期尼日利亚奈拉将继续遭受冲击，西非国家的企业寻求减少对美元的敞口，导致尼日利亚奈拉兑美元汇率跌至新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/-usd-ngn-nigerian-firms-slim-down-dollar-debt-as-naira-hits-another-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:48:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
