      <title>Amundi 看好瑞士法郎，押注其避险吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/amundi-turns-bullish-on-swiss-franc-in-bet-on-safe-haven-appeal</link>
